metadata.name: Scratched ClayPunks #2560
metadata.description:
Scratched ClayPunks are a Cryptopunks derivative collection independent from Yuga Labs. This work is our tribute to the iconic Cryptopunks collection.  
Each ClayPunk is made out of clay by the magical hands of artist CryptoClay and digitized in 3D. Scratched ClayPunks have the same attributes as original Cryptopunks and receive Proof-of-Work through www.scratch-tech.com technology: the SHA-256 hash of all Scratched ClayPunks images start with their serial numbers!
